brake hoses on a 1991 Ford Explorer. In this
step we're going to talk about the proper

00:00:11.300 --> 00:00:17.110
way to remount your vehicle's tire and the
proper method to snug down your vehicle's

00:00:17.110 --> 00:00:21.670
lug nuts. I've got my tire right here. Here
