00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:35.810
wheel flat and true and allows the self centering
mechanisms built into the rim and lug nuts

00:01:35.810 --> 00:01:48.630
to take effect. We're just snugging them now
we're going to torque them later.

00:01:48.630 --> 00:01:53.820
you can see why I like to use a four way because
